description:
In today’s episode, the boys conduct an intervention for Logan’s $200,000 Pokémon addiction, we open a rare pack of cards and hit the jackpot, discuss if it’s okay to get tea-bagged after talking a lot of sh*t (Adesanya vs. Costa), Logan has turned into the neighborhood KAREN, share our street fight stories, & for old times’ sake, we take a trip back to the 🍆 sand to talk about the 🐤 & 🐝 with our parents...
